
00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:10,040
[English subtitles are available.]



00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:22,520
[Episode 7]



00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:24,800
Don't fight!



00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:25,960
Calm down.



00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:27,160
Don't fight.



00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:28,960
I got it!



00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:30,320
That brat must have fled



00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,800
to the back of the hillside.



00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,200
I'll take you there.



00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:34,120
Hurry up.



00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:35,120
-After you.
-Let's go.



00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,200
Over here.



00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,079
This way, please.



00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:39,440
Tianqi.



00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:41,600
Are you sure Lu Ping will come here?



00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:45,120
I went to great lengths
to get this information.



00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:47,160
That brat always trains
at the back of the mountain.



00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:48,840
My father came to capture him.



00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,480
He is definitely hiding there.



00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,920
The last fight wasn't enough.



00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:53,360
I want to kill him this time.



00:02:55,160 --> 00:02:57,240
Tianqi. Someone is coming
from Zhaifeng Institute.



00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,200
Stay hidden.



00:02:58,600 --> 00:03:00,040
Don't make any sound.



00:03:00,440 --> 00:03:01,840
Once they are near, we'll make our move.



00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,040
Yes.



00:03:09,320 --> 00:03:10,120
Are you guys ready?



00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:36,800
Who did that?



00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,160
Brat!



00:03:39,320 --> 00:03:40,800
You didn't succumb
to the poison in the tower last time.



00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:41,960
I want to kill you today!



00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:55,400
Tianqi.



00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:57,800
Father, how could it be you?



00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:59,840
I sacrificed myself



00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,160
to save your father.



00:04:01,880 --> 00:04:03,120
Thank you.



00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:04,360
Am I dead?



00:04:04,440 --> 00:04:05,480
-Am I dead?
-No, you're not.



00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,440
You're still living.



00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,320
What's wrong?



00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,200
Why does it not hurt?



00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,800
I don't feel pain anymore.



00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:12,120
Hang on, you're...



00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:16,360
Get up right now.



00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,560
It's retribution for my sins.



00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:22,200
I originally wanted you two
to lead the attack



00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,320
and capture Lu Ping.



00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:25,880
Thank goodness, I walked in front of you.



00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:26,840
Otherwise,



00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:28,360
your son would have...



00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:29,960
Thank you so much.



00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:30,880
Are you okay?



00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:31,880
I'm fine.



00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:34,800
Mr. Wei, what did you mean just now?



00:04:35,200 --> 00:04:36,800
You used poison inside the tower.



00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:38,000
I didn't.



00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,560
Cheating in the exam



00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:41,720
and poisoning the lives
of other examinees.



00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:43,120
What kind of crime is this?



00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:46,680
Tianqi, don't be afraid!



00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,400
My son will never



00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,800
do such a despicable act.



00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:51,520
It was so chaotic just now.



00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:54,040
Maybe you heard it wrongly.



00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:56,320
All of us heard it.



00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,400
Your son did it.



00:04:58,320 --> 00:04:59,159
Yes!



00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:00,560
You guys heard it wrongly!



00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:01,800
They heard it wrongly.



00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:02,920
Everyone heard it wrongly!



00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:04,040
Yes, they heard it wrongly.



00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,120
We heard it, Master.



00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:06,040
We swear.



00:05:08,840 --> 00:05:09,920
Actually, I heard it too.



00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,360
You...



00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:12,280
How could you?



00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,600
Come over here.



00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:20,040
Well, I need a bit of hush money.



00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:21,280
We, Zhaifeng Institute,



00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:23,640
aren't as wealthy
as the Chan State Academy.



00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,040
We don't accept payment on credit.



00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:25,920
Cash.



00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:26,960
Cash is accepted.



00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:29,880
Guo Youdao.



00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:31,560
This is blackmail.



00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:33,200
You're blackmailing me.



00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:40,400
They are gone.



00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:41,720
Every single person



00:05:41,840 --> 00:05:43,520
from the Wei family left.



00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,000
I told you.



00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,920
My luck is back again.



00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:47,800
Really?



00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,000
Of course.



00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:56,600
Lu Ping.



00:05:57,880 --> 00:05:59,680
They left and we're fine now.



00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:04,840
Can we still go back?



00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:06,800
I already said those things.



00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:08,080
Going back is embarrassing.



00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:13,080
Come, let's wait for him
at Ruyu Restaurant.



00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:14,800
Who are we waiting for?



00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,680
After he arrives,



00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:18,280
you'll know.



00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:33,040
Master.



00:06:34,640 --> 00:06:36,600
Why did you protect Lu Ping desperately?



00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:38,440
You even pretended to be a bad person.



00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:43,840
No wonder Lu Ping always provokes you.



00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:46,880
Now, I also feel that



00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,440
your personality



00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:50,800
is quite interesting.



00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:09,120
Come with me.



00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:18,360
[Ruyu Restaurant]



00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:24,440
[From now on,]



00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:29,600
you have nothing to do
with Zhaifeng Institute.



00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:31,800
[Cutting ties with them]



00:07:32,400 --> 00:07:34,480
[is the only way to save them
from all this mess.]



00:07:36,840 --> 00:07:38,600
Lu Ping, he is really here.



00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:41,920
[Save me!]



00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,040
Mo Lin.



00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,120
Su Tang is your disciple



00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,159
and also my disciple.



00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:48,080
If I die,



00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:49,800
I'll never let her take you as her master.



00:07:51,520 --> 00:07:53,240
Speak now if you have something to say.



00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:54,480
You guys can either fight now



00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:55,640
or get this done with.



00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,840
Old geezer, I'm going to kill you.



00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:00,200
Master.



00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:02,720
Is this why you want me to come with you?



00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:03,960
Old geezer.



00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:05,840
I won't let you die instantly.



00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:07,880
The Piebald Scorpion Venom on this arrow



00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:10,120
will make you itch for 49 days.



00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,320
Despicable person!



00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,360
Come here if you dare...



00:08:16,280 --> 00:08:17,560
and fight with Xifan.



00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:19,240
Let go of Xifan if you dare.



00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:20,520
I'll never let him go.



00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:21,880
Lu Ping, come here.



00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:22,800
Perfect timing.



00:08:22,880 --> 00:08:24,680
Make that brat stop right now.



00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:26,080
Am I not rat poop?



00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:29,640
Assumed I farted loudly that day, can you?



00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:31,360
Please don't, Master.



00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:33,440
Although I'm petty,



00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,880
I really want to talk to you



00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,200
openly and honestly,



00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:40,440
so that you can understand me.



00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:45,600
Madam Jin.



00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:48,360
Prepare some dishes and wine.



00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,160
Put it on my bill.



00:08:51,880 --> 00:08:52,680
All right.



00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:56,800
Shi Dongchun wine?



00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,280
A pot costs 52 silver taels.



00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:02,440
One sip is worth three silver taels.



00:09:03,760 --> 00:09:06,400
After I finish it, it's gone after I pee.



00:09:08,560 --> 00:09:09,640
A fine wine



00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:12,720
deserves a modest master.



00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:15,080
If you didn't use tricks



00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:16,920
and wrote the letter to attract Qin Qi,



00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:20,240
I'm afraid I'm still trapped
in Chan State.



00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:31,360
Is your head messed up
after getting beaten inside the tower?



00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:33,760
I advise you to place your wager



00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,360
on someone else quickly.



00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:37,960
Someone else?



00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,080
I invested too much.



00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:46,040
If I withdraw halfway,
I'll lose everything.



00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:52,960
As long as I'm still
on the gambling table,



00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:55,680
I can recoup my losses.



00:10:14,040 --> 00:10:14,880
Now,



00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:18,800
we're disqualified
from the Soul Combat Convention.



00:10:19,400 --> 00:10:20,480
Where are you going next?



00:10:20,640 --> 00:10:21,720
I'll follow



00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,080
wherever Lu Ping goes.



00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,200
If we can't go to the convention,



00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:27,040
there is always another way.



00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,160
Why don't you dump



00:10:30,280 --> 00:10:32,000
your troublesome brother?



00:10:32,160 --> 00:10:33,080
Worship me as your master.



00:10:54,800 --> 00:10:55,840
You're not bad,



00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,720
but you shouldn't be with us.



00:10:58,400 --> 00:11:00,000
Don't you want
to roam the martial arts world



00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:01,360
and become the top assassin?



00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:04,480
Actually, I think you're quite impressive.



00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:06,280
Maybe next time when we meet,



00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:07,920
you've become the top assassin already.



00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:12,960
The next time we meet...



00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,480
Why do you look unhappy?



00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:19,720
I'm not.



00:11:20,560 --> 00:11:21,840
I just feel that...



00:11:25,040 --> 00:11:26,440
I couldn't get a disciple this time,



00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:29,280
so I'm feeling quite sad.



00:11:46,760 --> 00:11:48,800
Don't worry.



00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:54,360
You still have a chance.



00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:56,800
Su Tang.



00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:58,400
Do you know



00:11:58,560 --> 00:12:00,360
who is the important person



00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:03,360
I always visit every year at Kaifeng?



00:12:03,880 --> 00:12:04,840
Who is it?



00:12:12,040 --> 00:12:12,960
[Chu Min.]



00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:14,960
Tianzhao Academy's instructor?



00:12:15,520 --> 00:12:17,880
So, you visit her every year at Kaifeng.



00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:20,560
I can't believe an old man like you



00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:22,640
have such an influential friend.



00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:26,240
So you decided to stop calling me
an old geezer?



00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:28,040
Listen carefully.



00:12:29,640 --> 00:12:32,080
Soul Combat Convention requires
a team of four people to compete.



00:12:32,800 --> 00:12:33,880
The tower was demolished.



00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:35,800
Zhaifeng was already disqualified.



00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:38,280
But if you guys worship Chu Ming
as your master,



00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:41,760
we can use Tianzhao Academy's name



00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:43,000
to join the convention.



00:12:43,800 --> 00:12:44,880
Surpasses that of Beidou,



00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:45,920
make our ancestors proud.



00:12:46,040 --> 00:12:47,080
Both can be achieved.



00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:49,320
Lu Ping already agreed to it.



00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:52,320
If Lu Ping agrees, I agree too.



00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:54,880
Fine.



00:12:55,280 --> 00:12:57,080
I'll do this kind deed



00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:58,040
for my future disciple



00:12:58,120 --> 00:12:59,360
and let you guys owe me a favor.



00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:15,680
Please forgive me for not abiding.



00:13:28,320 --> 00:13:29,120
Master.



00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:30,760
Is Xifan okay?



00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:49,200
Xifan.



00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:56,200
Master.



00:13:57,360 --> 00:14:00,480
I saw you peeking just now.



00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:03,640
What's the matter?



00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:05,440
Are you feeling reluctant?



00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:06,880
Master.



00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:09,480
I know my own limits.



00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:14,120
I shouldn't be going
to the Soul Combat Convention.



00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:16,680
I'm not the one controlling your legs.



00:14:17,480 --> 00:14:19,160
I'm not stopping you anyway.



00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:23,920
An ambitious person needs a place



00:14:24,040 --> 00:14:25,800
to showcase his talent.



00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:28,960
You've stopped at Zhaifeng
for so many years.



00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:32,240
It's time for you to go back
to the path you belong on.



00:14:36,320 --> 00:14:37,760
I can't win against you.



00:14:38,880 --> 00:14:40,280
I can't even win against Lu Ping.



00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:42,920
I didn't atone for my sins.



00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,440
I can't hold a blade anymore.



00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:47,600
Even if I go to the convention,



00:14:48,520 --> 00:14:49,440
I can't be of help.



00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:50,720
Compared to you,



00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:52,080
Lu Ping is nothing.



00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:54,360
Without Zhaifeng Institute,



00:14:54,520 --> 00:14:55,960
Lu Ping won't be like this now.



00:14:56,080 --> 00:14:57,400
Without you,



00:14:57,480 --> 00:14:59,720
Zhaifeng won't be Zhaifeng.



00:15:04,960 --> 00:15:06,320
Xing Luo is dead.



00:15:09,280 --> 00:15:12,040
The weight is off your shoulders.



00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:13,560
Stop it, Master.



00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:16,200
My leg is injured.



00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:18,160
Whatever you say is pointless.



00:15:18,400 --> 00:15:19,920
It's too early to tell.



00:15:20,640 --> 00:15:22,040
Drink with me first.



00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:27,440
I can tell from one glance,



00:15:27,600 --> 00:15:29,640
that this Zhao Xifan is different
from you bumpkins.



00:15:30,040 --> 00:15:32,080
He has high self-esteem.



00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:34,280
This thing you made.



00:15:34,400 --> 00:15:36,800
Could it really make him
follow us to Kaifeng?



00:15:36,880 --> 00:15:37,760
Lu Ping.



00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:40,160
All these years,
after Xifan join Zhaifeng,



00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,800
he never returned home or went out.



00:15:41,920 --> 00:15:43,480
There's more to this than meets the eye.



00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:45,880
Didn't Master give you any advice?



00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:50,080
I think Master went drinking again.



00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:52,040
He didn't leave any message.



00:15:53,480 --> 00:15:54,840
After I make this,



00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:56,880
send this to him on my behalf.



00:15:57,920 --> 00:15:59,640
I provoked Xifan many times.



00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:02,440
It's better if you guys advise him.



00:16:04,760 --> 00:16:05,800
All of you are here.



00:16:06,760 --> 00:16:07,560
Lu Ping.



00:16:08,400 --> 00:16:10,520
When Master Guo bought wine, he left this.



00:16:11,160 --> 00:16:12,560
He said he's buying time for you



00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:14,120
and asked me to pass this to you.



00:16:15,040 --> 00:16:16,520
He also said,



00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:19,520
"the person who tied the bell..."



00:16:19,640 --> 00:16:20,480
Should untie it.



00:16:20,640 --> 00:16:21,680
"...should untie it."



00:16:22,200 --> 00:16:23,600
Why are you holding the boards?



00:16:26,680 --> 00:16:28,440
Isn't this Ruyu Restaurant's chair?



00:16:28,560 --> 00:16:29,880
Why did it become like this?



00:16:34,400 --> 00:16:35,920
It's pretty comfortable.



00:16:45,840 --> 00:16:46,640
Master.



00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:48,240
I should go now.



00:16:48,320 --> 00:16:49,280
Don't.



00:16:49,720 --> 00:16:51,120
Don't leave me.



00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:55,080
You completely ignored my feelings.



00:16:57,240 --> 00:16:59,240
Zhaifeng offended
the Wei family this time.



00:16:59,360 --> 00:17:01,680
If we don't get a placing
in the convention,



00:17:04,800 --> 00:17:06,040
the centuries-old organization



00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:08,640
will be ruined.



00:17:09,240 --> 00:17:11,319
Xifan, why don't you reconsider it?



00:17:11,440 --> 00:17:12,680
Can you?



00:17:12,760 --> 00:17:14,800
Master, I surrendered the badge.



00:17:15,079 --> 00:17:16,760
You should give it
to a more suitable person.



00:17:17,359 --> 00:17:18,160
Xifan.



00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:20,800
I have something to return to you.



00:17:21,079 --> 00:17:21,920
Here.



00:17:25,359 --> 00:17:26,960
I already gave it back to Master.



00:17:27,359 --> 00:17:29,000
The eldest disciple is
Zhaifeng's role model.



00:17:29,720 --> 00:17:30,600
Take it, God of Bandits.



00:17:30,680 --> 00:17:31,480
Nope.



00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:32,760
It's worthless.



00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:34,560
-Even if it's a gift, I won't take it.
-You...



00:17:36,320 --> 00:17:37,240
Xifan.



00:17:37,440 --> 00:17:38,520
It suits you more.



00:17:38,640 --> 00:17:39,440
Without you,



00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:42,440
I won't be where I am now.



00:17:44,040 --> 00:17:45,000
I have my past.



00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:46,800
You have your past too.



00:17:47,480 --> 00:17:48,520
Rather than running away,



00:17:49,280 --> 00:17:50,480
why don't we face it together?



00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:52,360
Yes.



00:17:56,720 --> 00:17:58,640
You said your personal matters
are none of my business.



00:17:59,360 --> 00:18:00,400
You can take it back now.



00:18:00,560 --> 00:18:02,200
I never take my words back.



00:18:03,040 --> 00:18:04,480
Let's get to know each other again.



00:18:05,560 --> 00:18:06,480
Wait for me.



00:18:06,680 --> 00:18:07,840
I have something for you.



00:18:28,760 --> 00:18:30,040
Your craftsmanship is pretty good.



00:18:30,840 --> 00:18:32,120
Come over here, give it a try.



00:18:33,200 --> 00:18:34,400
Here.



00:18:37,360 --> 00:18:38,160
Here.



00:18:43,520 --> 00:18:44,320
Hold them.



00:18:47,520 --> 00:18:48,880
There's hope



00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:50,760
to surpass Beidou!



00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,200
Move forward!



00:18:55,040 --> 00:18:56,160
Lu Ping, push him.



00:18:56,280 --> 00:18:57,280
Did you not eat?



00:19:14,760 --> 00:19:15,880
Chan State reported



00:19:16,320 --> 00:19:17,920
that you're dead.



00:19:22,040 --> 00:19:23,680
I have important news



00:19:24,040 --> 00:19:25,760
to inform our lord immediately.



00:19:34,440 --> 00:19:36,880
I was heavily injured
by the people of Zhaifeng.



00:19:37,480 --> 00:19:39,520
I only dared to show myself
after hiding for several days.



00:19:39,920 --> 00:19:41,000
What a useless junk.



00:19:41,680 --> 00:19:42,640
You embarrassed us!



00:19:43,320 --> 00:19:44,520
Why don't I pluck your teeth



00:19:44,640 --> 00:19:45,760
and make a necklace?



00:19:45,920 --> 00:19:47,480
The person concerns our lord's grand plan.



00:19:51,520 --> 00:19:53,640
I rushed back to report this.



00:19:54,160 --> 00:19:55,360
I'm very sure



00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:57,280
that the person is the Awakener,



00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:59,400
who was kidnapped from the tower
three years ago,



00:19:59,560 --> 00:20:00,520
Lu Ping.



00:20:06,120 --> 00:20:07,720
Did you see him clearly?



00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:08,800
Yes.



00:20:09,520 --> 00:20:10,840
I also heard



00:20:11,360 --> 00:20:14,520
that he's heading towards Kaifeng
for the Soul Combat Convention.



00:20:17,080 --> 00:20:18,920
I'm willing to go to great lengths



00:20:19,120 --> 00:20:20,240
to capture him,



00:20:20,800 --> 00:20:22,080
so I can redeem myself.



00:20:22,880 --> 00:20:23,800
It's fine.



00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:26,680
Since he already showed himself,



00:20:26,840 --> 00:20:28,280
he won't be able to escape again.



00:20:29,600 --> 00:20:32,280
Nobody can walk away from Shanhai Gang.



00:20:32,920 --> 00:20:35,400
Dying here is his destiny.



00:20:38,680 --> 00:20:39,800
As for you,



00:20:40,600 --> 00:20:42,800
you should know the rules of Shanhai Gang.



00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:45,000
Take her away.



00:20:55,120 --> 00:20:57,400
How is the arrangement at Kaifeng?



00:20:58,160 --> 00:21:00,320
Mr. Feng has made
the necessary preparations.



00:21:00,560 --> 00:21:02,800
Your plan may begin at any time.



00:21:04,920 --> 00:21:05,800
Pass my order.



00:21:06,320 --> 00:21:07,800
Don't act rashly and alert the enemy.



00:21:07,880 --> 00:21:08,680
Yes.



00:21:22,640 --> 00:21:25,320
The triennial Soul Combat Convention
is around the corner.



00:21:25,840 --> 00:21:28,360
How is the preparation, Mr. Wen?



00:21:28,520 --> 00:21:29,440
Your Majesty.



00:21:29,840 --> 00:21:32,120
I already negotiated with General Qin



00:21:32,480 --> 00:21:34,840
and sent invitations
to all martial arts academy



00:21:35,080 --> 00:21:36,920
to recruit talented people
from across the kingdom,



00:21:37,040 --> 00:21:38,480
so we can contribute to the kingdom.



00:21:39,600 --> 00:21:40,400
Your Majesty.



00:21:40,680 --> 00:21:44,960
In my opinion,
Mr. Wen's actions were inappropriate.



00:21:46,520 --> 00:21:48,800
Mr. Xia, why do you say so?



00:21:49,880 --> 00:21:52,800
The selection of generals
concern the strength,



00:21:52,960 --> 00:21:54,280
the rise, and fall of the kingdom.



00:21:54,960 --> 00:21:56,440
For generals of Shuo Kingdom,



00:21:56,560 --> 00:21:59,000
we should select them
from prominent families by right.



00:21:59,400 --> 00:22:01,360
Your Majesty,
a hero's origin isn't important.



00:22:01,520 --> 00:22:04,680
There are many extraordinary people
in the martial arts world.



00:22:04,920 --> 00:22:06,240
If we miss out on them,



00:22:06,400 --> 00:22:07,960
it will be Shuo Kingdom's loss.



00:22:08,760 --> 00:22:09,880
In terms of talent,



00:22:10,360 --> 00:22:12,000
many disciples of Tianzhao Academy



00:22:12,120 --> 00:22:14,360
have been enlisted over the years.



00:22:14,640 --> 00:22:16,880
All of them are excellent in martial arts.



00:22:17,360 --> 00:22:18,160
In terms of loyalty,



00:22:18,680 --> 00:22:21,640
imperial relatives come
after prominent families.



00:22:21,800 --> 00:22:22,920
Their loyalty was indisputable.



00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:27,040
How could the martial artists
fare against them?



00:22:27,520 --> 00:22:28,960
I think that,



00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:31,720
General Qin has many acquaintances
in the martial arts world,



00:22:31,960 --> 00:22:34,320
especially the people
with an unclear background



00:22:34,440 --> 00:22:36,120
and a suspicious motive.



00:22:36,320 --> 00:22:38,840
It's a disgrace to Shuo Kingdom.



00:22:39,080 --> 00:22:41,320
Mr. Xia is also the headmaster
of Tianzhao Academy.



00:22:41,480 --> 00:22:43,920
Naturally, your disciples' capability
can't be underestimated.



00:22:44,520 --> 00:22:45,360
But in my opinion,



00:22:45,560 --> 00:22:46,440
gathering talented people



00:22:46,600 --> 00:22:47,520
from all walks of life



00:22:47,680 --> 00:22:49,800
is the only root of serving
the imperial family.



00:22:50,160 --> 00:22:52,800
If you're afraid that commoners
will overshadow the imperial family,



00:22:52,960 --> 00:22:55,200
doesn't this goes
against the imperial graciousness?



00:22:57,600 --> 00:22:59,320
General, you just returned.



00:22:59,480 --> 00:23:01,080
You should take off your armor first.



00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:02,160
While I'm absent,



00:23:02,360 --> 00:23:04,320
Mr. Xia won't waste this opportunity.



00:23:04,720 --> 00:23:06,520
I can't let Mr. Wen suffer alone.



00:23:08,000 --> 00:23:09,400
My two officials,



00:23:09,800 --> 00:23:12,400
you've been planning
for this martial arts event.



00:23:12,880 --> 00:23:14,240
You want the best for the kingdom.



00:23:15,160 --> 00:23:16,280
Please don't be agitated.



00:23:17,120 --> 00:23:17,920
Your Majesty.



00:23:18,040 --> 00:23:22,400
[Commander of Victorious Dragon Troop,
Qin Qi requests to meet.]



00:23:23,480 --> 00:23:24,280
Summon him.



00:23:33,680 --> 00:23:34,880
Greetings, Your Majesty.



00:23:36,040 --> 00:23:38,360
General Qin, you must've had
a tiring journey.



00:23:38,560 --> 00:23:39,480
Serving the kingdom



00:23:39,640 --> 00:23:40,640
is my pleasure.



00:23:41,480 --> 00:23:42,280
Your Majesty.



00:23:42,560 --> 00:23:44,000
I heard the martial arts academy



00:23:44,120 --> 00:23:46,600
are planning to send their disciples
to take part in this convention.



00:23:46,880 --> 00:23:48,000
Shuo Kingdom's martial artists



00:23:48,160 --> 00:23:49,600
have never been gathered together.



00:23:50,040 --> 00:23:51,960
It's the blessing of Shuo Kingdom.



00:23:52,600 --> 00:23:54,920
I'm afraid Mr. Xia doesn't believe so.



00:23:56,680 --> 00:23:58,280
Does Mr. Xia still believe



00:23:58,600 --> 00:24:01,200
that generals should be
from prominent families?



00:24:01,920 --> 00:24:02,800
Exactly so.



00:24:03,360 --> 00:24:05,240
Your Qin family is prominent.



00:24:05,400 --> 00:24:06,560
They are valiant.



00:24:07,160 --> 00:24:08,080
They have also cultivated



00:24:08,240 --> 00:24:10,080
a talented person like General Qin.



00:24:10,640 --> 00:24:11,920
This proves my point.



00:24:12,200 --> 00:24:13,880
Lieutenant general
of Left Guard Corps, Li Che,



00:24:14,080 --> 00:24:15,600
graduated from Chan State Academy.



00:24:16,080 --> 00:24:18,080
Since he took office
to suppress the northwestern bandits,



00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:20,400
he performed a total
of 35 meritorious services.



00:24:20,880 --> 00:24:22,880
Lieutenant general
of Imperial Martial Artists, Fang Qiong



00:24:23,120 --> 00:24:24,600
graduated from Xu State Academy.



00:24:24,840 --> 00:24:26,000
This person was a genius.



00:24:26,240 --> 00:24:28,680
He invented Horse Splitting Formation
and fought countless enemies.



00:24:29,200 --> 00:24:31,200
Since Mr. Wen takes control
of the army selection,



00:24:31,360 --> 00:24:32,800
many generals selected



00:24:33,000 --> 00:24:34,920
from the commoners are talented.



00:24:35,560 --> 00:24:37,920
But some people from prominent families



00:24:38,680 --> 00:24:40,360
are incompetent and corrupted.



00:24:41,040 --> 00:24:44,360
I believe Mr. Xia knows this clearly.



00:24:45,480 --> 00:24:46,440
More importantly,



00:24:46,640 --> 00:24:48,240
the citizens are in turmoil
over the years.



00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:49,200
There is unrest.



00:24:49,720 --> 00:24:51,440
The citizens are fighting
against oppression.



00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:53,080
If we can unite the citizens



00:24:53,240 --> 00:24:54,680
and put them to good use



00:24:54,960 --> 00:24:56,360
through the Soul Combat Convention,



00:24:56,560 --> 00:24:59,280
we won't have to worry about
Shuo Kingdom's prosperity and stability.



00:25:02,280 --> 00:25:03,080
Your Majesty.



00:25:03,440 --> 00:25:04,560
Forgive my bluntness.



00:25:04,840 --> 00:25:05,720
During this convention,



00:25:05,880 --> 00:25:07,600
you're not only selecting generals,



00:25:07,880 --> 00:25:10,760
you're also raising the ambitious
and fighting spirit of the kingdom.



00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:12,160
Nicely spoken.



00:25:14,960 --> 00:25:16,480
This Soul Combat Convention



00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:19,560
is to enlighten the soul power
of Shuo Kingdom.



00:25:20,160 --> 00:25:21,000
General Qin.



00:25:21,720 --> 00:25:24,440
I'm looking forward



00:25:25,360 --> 00:25:28,680
to the kind of talented heroes



00:25:28,880 --> 00:25:30,160
you and Mr. Wen will select



00:25:30,600 --> 00:25:32,640
during this Soul Combat Convention.



00:25:35,440 --> 00:25:37,720
We won't disappoint Your Majesty.



00:25:43,920 --> 00:25:44,960
General Qin.



00:25:50,160 --> 00:25:51,000
General Qin.



00:25:51,520 --> 00:25:54,800
You sounded sure of yourself
in the court today.



00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:56,720
But I still hope



00:25:56,960 --> 00:25:59,560
that the martial artists you recommend



00:25:59,800 --> 00:26:01,320
can be like you too,



00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:03,080
so His Majesty won't disappoint.



00:26:03,160 --> 00:26:06,600
Please look forward to it then, Mr. Xia.



00:26:21,640 --> 00:26:22,440
Wenrui.



00:26:23,120 --> 00:26:24,240
I'll send Mr. Wen home.



00:26:24,680 --> 00:26:26,240
Find a director for a check-up.



00:26:26,320 --> 00:26:27,120
Yes.



00:26:27,560 --> 00:26:28,400
I'm fine, General.



00:26:28,760 --> 00:26:30,440
It's just a relapse of my old injury.



00:26:31,600 --> 00:26:32,880
In the court just now,



00:26:33,320 --> 00:26:35,880
thank you for fighting for me.



00:26:36,480 --> 00:26:37,320
But at this rate,



00:26:37,520 --> 00:26:39,600
the hatred between Mr. Xia
and you grows deeper.



00:26:39,840 --> 00:26:41,160
Since there's already a grudge,



00:26:41,720 --> 00:26:44,080
leave it be if I can't resolve it.



00:26:45,800 --> 00:26:46,640
General.



00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:49,520
You should plan for your own future.



00:26:50,080 --> 00:26:52,000
I'm just an ordinary guy
from the martial arts world.



00:26:52,680 --> 00:26:54,000
Don't worry about me.



00:26:54,320 --> 00:26:55,120
Mr. Wen.



00:26:56,040 --> 00:26:56,960
All these years,



00:26:57,080 --> 00:26:58,640
If you didn't discuss martial arts with me



00:26:58,800 --> 00:27:00,040
and organize military affairs,



00:27:00,360 --> 00:27:02,440
you won't become a thorn
in Xia Bojian's flesh.



00:27:02,760 --> 00:27:03,560
Not to mention,



00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:05,880
if I protect you,
I also protect the talented people



00:27:06,040 --> 00:27:07,840
who will work for Shuo Kingdom
in the future.



00:27:08,640 --> 00:27:09,960
Do you still remember what I said



00:27:10,480 --> 00:27:12,560
when we were organizing
the Soul Combat Convention



00:27:12,760 --> 00:27:13,760
back then, Mr. Wen?



00:27:14,800 --> 00:27:15,640
I still remember.



00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:18,600
"The Qin family conquered the world
with the previous emperor.



00:27:18,840 --> 00:27:21,160
Knowing that soldiers
are the roots of a kingdom,



00:27:21,880 --> 00:27:24,400
if I can bring talented martial artists
to Shuo Kingdom,



00:27:24,720 --> 00:27:26,440
even if I have to go against
the whole world,



00:27:26,840 --> 00:27:29,000
I, Qin Qi, am not afraid."



00:27:31,720 --> 00:27:34,520
I'm amazed by your lofty spirit.



00:27:34,880 --> 00:27:37,080
I'll definitely handle
the Soul Combat Convention,



00:27:37,280 --> 00:27:38,800
so I'll live up to your expectations.



00:27:39,640 --> 00:27:40,640
Come with me now.



00:27:40,800 --> 00:27:42,320
After you rest well,



00:27:42,800 --> 00:27:44,920
the Soul Combat Convention
needs you as a host.



00:27:45,800 --> 00:27:46,800
Also,



00:27:47,360 --> 00:27:48,200
Qin Sang...



00:27:49,280 --> 00:27:50,840
Qin Sang has been wanting to meet you.



00:27:52,120 --> 00:27:54,440
Did Ms. Qin create
some sort of trouble again



00:27:54,640 --> 00:27:55,960
and you need to deal with it?



00:28:03,000 --> 00:28:04,000
I instructed you guys.



00:28:04,160 --> 00:28:05,080
Don't hold back.



00:28:05,240 --> 00:28:06,960
All of you are pulling your punches.



00:28:07,280 --> 00:28:08,760
What's the point of fighting?



00:28:09,280 --> 00:28:10,160
Dismiss.



00:28:11,480 --> 00:28:12,360
Yes.



00:28:12,880 --> 00:28:14,160
You fought three people previously.



00:28:14,560 --> 00:28:15,920
Now, you can fight five people.



00:28:16,400 --> 00:28:17,480
It seems you've made progress.



00:28:18,400 --> 00:28:20,200
I heard that when you were at my age,



00:28:20,400 --> 00:28:21,520
you can fight ten people.



00:28:22,120 --> 00:28:23,720
Why don't you train with me?



00:28:24,600 --> 00:28:26,440
When I train the Sun Streamer Swordplay
with Ziyan,



00:28:26,600 --> 00:28:27,720
she always holds back.



00:28:27,960 --> 00:28:28,960
It's suffocating.



00:28:29,360 --> 00:28:30,400
Ziyan!



00:28:34,560 --> 00:28:35,680
You instructed me before



00:28:35,760 --> 00:28:36,920
that I can't train with Miss.



00:28:37,080 --> 00:28:38,160
I have crossed the line.



00:28:38,360 --> 00:28:39,600
Please forgive me.



00:28:46,560 --> 00:28:47,920
I ordered Ziyan.



00:28:51,640 --> 00:28:53,520
I know the Sun Streamer Swordplay
can't be divulged,



00:28:53,720 --> 00:28:55,520
but I need someone
to counter my moves, don't I?



00:28:55,720 --> 00:28:56,880
You love roaming the world.



00:28:57,040 --> 00:28:57,960
I allowed you.



00:28:58,400 --> 00:28:59,320
The Sun Streamer Swordplay



00:28:59,480 --> 00:29:00,960
is the Qin family's
secret sword technique.



00:29:01,400 --> 00:29:02,240
Once it's divulged,



00:29:02,440 --> 00:29:03,920
it disturbs our clan's foundation.



00:29:04,200 --> 00:29:06,040
Did you totally ignore what I said?



00:29:09,080 --> 00:29:11,760
You two, accept your punishments
based on the family rules.



00:29:14,560 --> 00:29:15,400
Go now!



00:29:20,240 --> 00:29:21,160
Don't get angry, General.



00:29:21,720 --> 00:29:23,240
Let me be the mediator.



00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:25,320
Soul Combat Convention is upon us.



00:29:25,840 --> 00:29:27,760
Why don't we make a deal here?



00:29:28,360 --> 00:29:29,960
If Ms. Qin wins the convention,



00:29:30,200 --> 00:29:33,120
Ms. Ling's and her punishments
will be revoked.



00:29:33,360 --> 00:29:34,680
If Ms. Qin didn't manage to pass,



00:29:34,920 --> 00:29:37,320
she'll accept your punishment
without any objection.



00:29:37,680 --> 00:29:38,760
What do you think?



00:29:39,480 --> 00:29:40,400
-Mr. Wen...
-All right!



00:29:40,840 --> 00:29:41,680
It's just a convention.



00:29:41,880 --> 00:29:43,160
I'll win and show it to you.



00:29:43,960 --> 00:29:45,400
What do you think, General?



00:29:48,320 --> 00:29:49,160
Fine.



00:29:49,960 --> 00:29:51,440
She won't listen to anyone,



00:29:51,800 --> 00:29:52,880
but only to Mr. Wen.



00:29:53,520 --> 00:29:54,680
But let me tell you.



00:29:55,320 --> 00:29:57,360
Don't expect Mr. Wen to cheat for you.



00:29:57,840 --> 00:30:00,160
If you want to win,
you must rely on your own strength.



00:30:00,360 --> 00:30:02,520
If I ask Mr. Wen to guide me
in martial arts,



00:30:02,720 --> 00:30:03,840
it's not cheating, right?



00:30:04,320 --> 00:30:05,360
Mr. Wen, come with me.



00:30:14,080 --> 00:30:14,920
Mr. Wen.



00:30:15,320 --> 00:30:16,680
You're the most knowledgeable.



00:30:17,240 --> 00:30:18,680
Have you heard of a chain



00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:20,720
that can bind one's soul power?



00:30:22,760 --> 00:30:25,600
Why did you suddenly ask this, Miss?



00:30:26,520 --> 00:30:27,360
Do you know?



00:30:27,800 --> 00:30:29,440
Do you know how to unbind it?



00:30:30,880 --> 00:30:31,960
Indeed, there's



00:30:32,160 --> 00:30:34,560
a blood martial art
called Soul Confinement.



00:30:35,000 --> 00:30:36,760
But it's rare and complicated.



00:30:37,080 --> 00:30:39,400
As to whether it can be unbound,



00:30:39,640 --> 00:30:41,920
it depends on the person.



00:30:42,800 --> 00:30:45,200
Have you seen this kind of martial arts?



00:31:02,960 --> 00:31:05,360
[Why am I concerned about that rogue?]



00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:08,280
[I must concentrate]



00:31:08,480 --> 00:31:09,840
[to train my swordsmanship.]



00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:11,920
[I must perform well]



00:31:12,120 --> 00:31:13,760
[during the Soul Combat Convention.]



00:31:16,560 --> 00:31:17,880
I heard it from a young bandit.



00:31:18,680 --> 00:31:20,320
Mr. Wen, I'll get a cup of tea for you.



00:31:20,520 --> 00:31:21,640
Let's continue training later.



00:31:41,240 --> 00:31:42,880
"Preparations are made in Kaifeng.



00:31:43,280 --> 00:31:45,280
Our lord orders you
to stop chasing after Lu Ping.



00:31:45,520 --> 00:31:47,000
Stay in Chan State for further orders.



00:31:47,280 --> 00:31:48,360
Failing again



00:31:48,880 --> 00:31:49,880
won't be forgivable."



00:31:50,720 --> 00:31:52,320
How gracious of our lord.



00:31:52,480 --> 00:31:53,560
It's not our time yet.



00:31:54,280 --> 00:31:56,160
The Wei family is safe for now.



00:31:56,440 --> 00:31:57,240
What about our future?



00:31:57,800 --> 00:31:59,600
Let's take one step at a time.



00:32:00,320 --> 00:32:03,320
Our lives are in the hands of others.



00:32:04,880 --> 00:32:05,680
Father.



00:32:07,360 --> 00:32:08,800
Father, I've decided.



00:32:09,520 --> 00:32:12,000
Father, why are you sweating?



00:32:13,240 --> 00:32:15,080
The weather is so hot. It's too stuffy.



00:32:15,280 --> 00:32:16,240
What do you need?



00:32:16,400 --> 00:32:18,120
I want to go to Kaifeng
for the convention.



00:32:18,240 --> 00:32:19,200
If I'm famous,



00:32:19,280 --> 00:32:20,320
I'll be worthy of Sangsang.



00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:21,680
Young Master.



00:32:22,240 --> 00:32:23,560
Go if you must.



00:32:23,920 --> 00:32:24,720
Wei Ming.



00:32:24,840 --> 00:32:26,080
Let Wei Ying bring the bodyguards



00:32:26,280 --> 00:32:28,200
with the best martial arts
to protect Young Master.



00:32:28,280 --> 00:32:29,080
Thank you, Father.



00:32:29,320 --> 00:32:30,520
I'll write a letter now.



00:32:30,720 --> 00:32:31,800
I want to tell Sangsang.



00:32:38,360 --> 00:32:39,160
Master.



00:32:39,840 --> 00:32:41,120
Lu Ping is at Kaifeng too.



00:32:41,720 --> 00:32:43,200
It's better to avoid him right now.



00:32:44,040 --> 00:32:46,160
The Shanhai Gang's punishment
is hanging over our heads.



00:32:46,360 --> 00:32:48,640
We are walking on thin ice.



00:32:48,840 --> 00:32:50,800
Let Tianqi do whatever he wants.



00:32:51,280 --> 00:32:53,440
The Shanhai Gang
treats Lu Ping indifferently.



00:32:53,640 --> 00:32:56,400
Tell Wei Ying to protect Tianqi this time.



00:32:56,600 --> 00:32:59,120
Don't let him get involved with Lu Ping.



00:32:59,680 --> 00:33:00,640
Yes.



00:33:19,000 --> 00:33:19,840
I can't.



00:33:20,000 --> 00:33:21,400
I can't walk anymore.



00:33:29,400 --> 00:33:30,240
Guo Youdao.



00:33:30,360 --> 00:33:32,240
Didn't you take a lot of silver taels
from Wei Zhong?



00:33:32,360 --> 00:33:33,760
Can't you hire a carriage?



00:33:34,720 --> 00:33:36,120
How dare you.



00:33:36,640 --> 00:33:38,480
The martial arts tower was so expensive.



00:33:39,240 --> 00:33:40,920
I gave them to Chan State Academy.



00:33:41,600 --> 00:33:43,920
Be thankful that we don't have
to beg for food.



00:33:44,720 --> 00:33:45,640
Martial arts practitioners



00:33:45,760 --> 00:33:46,960
shouldn't crave for comfort.



00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:48,160
It's easy for you to talk.



00:33:48,360 --> 00:33:49,320
You've been sitting.



00:33:49,440 --> 00:33:50,800
My disciple was pushing you.



00:33:51,960 --> 00:33:52,800
Mo Lin.



00:33:53,520 --> 00:33:55,000
Do you want to sleep here



00:33:55,640 --> 00:33:57,000
or do you want to sleep on a bed



00:33:57,080 --> 00:33:58,600
in Kaifeng City with a full stomach?



00:34:07,800 --> 00:34:09,199
Isn't this Ms. Qin's golden badge?



00:34:09,280 --> 00:34:10,080
Lu Ping.



00:34:10,199 --> 00:34:11,400
Let's go to Kaifeng quickly.



00:34:11,480 --> 00:34:12,760
Stay in the most luxurious inn.



00:34:14,000 --> 00:34:14,800
-Yes.
-No!



00:34:15,480 --> 00:34:16,960
Using someone's name to deceive people,



00:34:17,159 --> 00:34:18,560
how is it different from stealing?



00:34:18,639 --> 00:34:19,440
Xifan.



00:34:19,639 --> 00:34:20,600
Even if he's poor,



00:34:20,920 --> 00:34:22,400
he can't give up on his principles.



00:34:22,560 --> 00:34:23,400
Look at him.



00:34:23,480 --> 00:34:25,360
Zhaifeng disciples must be honorable.



00:34:25,600 --> 00:34:27,120
Master, this is what you taught us.



00:34:27,199 --> 00:34:28,000
What should we eat?



00:34:28,120 --> 00:34:28,920
We must eat chicken.



00:34:29,159 --> 00:34:30,000
Yes.



00:34:30,080 --> 00:34:30,920
Yes.



00:34:31,600 --> 00:34:32,400
Let me think about it.



00:34:33,560 --> 00:34:35,080
One whole chicken isn't enough.



00:34:35,280 --> 00:34:36,360
I can eat half a chicken.



00:34:36,520 --> 00:34:37,440
Let's order two then.



00:34:48,440 --> 00:34:51,239
[Tianzhao Academy]



00:34:53,600 --> 00:34:55,920
Miss, it has been a while
since you return to Tianzhao.



00:34:56,120 --> 00:34:57,360
But you refused to enter.



00:34:57,560 --> 00:34:59,080
Don't you want to visit your peers?



00:35:00,320 --> 00:35:01,120
Ziyan.



00:35:01,840 --> 00:35:02,880
I was here for three years.



00:35:03,440 --> 00:35:05,400
But I attended classes
for less than three months.



00:35:05,800 --> 00:35:07,000
Do you know why?



00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:12,760
Tianzhao only accepts disciples
from prominent families.



00:35:13,200 --> 00:35:14,440
It's not about martial arts,



00:35:14,680 --> 00:35:15,800
but one's family background.



00:35:17,720 --> 00:35:18,680
This type of place



00:35:19,160 --> 00:35:20,960
isn't as interesting
as Zhaifeng Institute.



00:35:23,280 --> 00:35:24,280
Qin Sang.



00:35:26,640 --> 00:35:27,560
Luo Ting.



00:35:29,000 --> 00:35:29,920
Congratulations.



00:35:30,160 --> 00:35:31,320
For the Soul Combat Convention,



00:35:31,560 --> 00:35:33,400
you and I are selected.



00:35:33,640 --> 00:35:36,080
I wonder if you're interested
in forming a team.



00:35:37,040 --> 00:35:38,240
Thank you for the kind offer.



00:35:38,760 --> 00:35:41,320
Ziyan and I will find two more disciples.



00:35:41,840 --> 00:35:44,000
You are highly respected in Tianzhao.



00:35:44,320 --> 00:35:46,160
I believe you have better candidates.



00:35:50,000 --> 00:35:51,040
A slave



00:35:51,640 --> 00:35:53,080
who become



00:35:53,320 --> 00:35:55,360
a disciple of Tianzhao to protect you.



00:35:56,000 --> 00:35:57,560
She's not worth it.



00:35:58,240 --> 00:35:59,720
Plus, I heard that you returned



00:35:59,960 --> 00:36:01,640
from experiencing the martial arts world.



00:36:02,000 --> 00:36:04,040
You're from a prominent family after all.



00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:06,200
Roaming among commoners
in the martial arts world



00:36:06,400 --> 00:36:07,560
goes against the decorum.



00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:10,480
Why don't you mingle with us?



00:36:10,720 --> 00:36:12,520
That's only fitting for your identity.



00:36:16,440 --> 00:36:18,920
I don't care about one's identity.



00:36:19,440 --> 00:36:21,120
I only look at one's martial arts.



00:36:21,720 --> 00:36:22,920
Plus, the martial artists



00:36:23,120 --> 00:36:24,120
come from all walks of life.



00:36:24,520 --> 00:36:26,040
There's no shortage of talented people.



00:36:26,920 --> 00:36:28,840
Since you're going
to the Soul Combat Convention,



00:36:29,160 --> 00:36:30,880
you'll witness it soon.



00:36:33,320 --> 00:36:35,000
Ziyan, let's go.



00:36:41,600 --> 00:36:44,400
Luo Ting, you're from a prominent family,



00:36:44,680 --> 00:36:46,160
Headmaster Xia's favorite disciple.



00:36:46,720 --> 00:36:49,240
If the Qin family didn't organize
the Soul Combat Convention,



00:36:49,520 --> 00:36:51,320
you already joined the military
as an official.



00:36:51,720 --> 00:36:54,440
You won't have to fight
with those martial artists.



00:36:54,880 --> 00:36:57,200
You're broad-minded
so you chose not to argue with her.



00:36:57,920 --> 00:36:59,120
But she has gotten worse.



00:36:59,480 --> 00:37:01,240
She said you're worse than her maid.



00:37:03,080 --> 00:37:07,280
[Hongfu Inn]



00:37:28,880 --> 00:37:29,920
If I know the Qin family



00:37:30,120 --> 00:37:31,440
is so powerful in Kaifeng,



00:37:31,600 --> 00:37:32,440
I should've asked



00:37:32,640 --> 00:37:34,600
for double the price
from Qin Sang back then.



00:37:35,360 --> 00:37:36,200
At this point in time,



00:37:36,400 --> 00:37:37,600
do you still want to kill Lu Ping?



00:37:38,240 --> 00:37:39,240
No way.



00:37:39,480 --> 00:37:41,600
How can I touch our boss?



00:37:42,120 --> 00:37:42,920
Right, Su Tang.



00:37:43,160 --> 00:37:44,280
Do you like this room?



00:37:44,520 --> 00:37:45,560
It's the most expensive.



00:37:45,800 --> 00:37:47,320
I have a good taste after all.



00:37:49,200 --> 00:37:50,000
All right.



00:37:50,640 --> 00:37:53,080
Let's keep this room for Lu Ping.



00:37:55,080 --> 00:37:55,880
Where is Lu Ping?



00:38:07,280 --> 00:38:08,520
If you don't change the dressing,



00:38:09,200 --> 00:38:11,080
don't dream of walking again.



00:38:12,560 --> 00:38:14,320
Did you cheat
using Qin family's golden badge?



00:38:14,600 --> 00:38:15,400
Do you not need this?



00:38:16,000 --> 00:38:16,800
I don't need it.



00:38:17,320 --> 00:38:18,120
All right.



00:38:18,960 --> 00:38:19,800
Lu Ping.



00:38:20,480 --> 00:38:22,520
Don't you want
to fight against Shanhai Gang?



00:38:22,960 --> 00:38:24,240
Can you change your bad habits



00:38:24,320 --> 00:38:25,120
and be a good person?



00:38:25,240 --> 00:38:26,200
Xifan.



00:38:27,240 --> 00:38:28,560
Good people will not only die,



00:38:28,960 --> 00:38:30,200
but they will die earlier.



00:38:30,880 --> 00:38:31,760
This is the principle.



00:38:34,040 --> 00:38:35,640
When you can walk on your own,



00:38:35,920 --> 00:38:37,240
let's talk about your principles.



00:38:38,200 --> 00:38:39,120
Lu Ping!



00:38:40,440 --> 00:38:41,240
Master.



00:38:41,320 --> 00:38:42,960
Lu Ping, take a look inside.



00:38:43,120 --> 00:38:44,600
The interior is so luxurious.



00:38:45,240 --> 00:38:46,120
Hurry up.



00:38:53,120 --> 00:38:53,920
Looking at you,



00:38:54,120 --> 00:38:56,160
it seems you're determined
to sleep outside.



00:38:56,560 --> 00:39:00,120
I have never stayed in such a nice inn.



00:39:00,360 --> 00:39:01,640
I won't accompany you.



00:39:02,280 --> 00:39:03,080
Master!



00:39:07,680 --> 00:39:08,520
Help me up.



00:39:17,720 --> 00:39:19,960
Did you change your mind?



00:39:20,200 --> 00:39:21,280
If I don't rest well



00:39:21,400 --> 00:39:22,440
and get back on my feet,



00:39:22,640 --> 00:39:24,640
that guy, Lu Ping is going
to be on cloud nine.



00:39:33,640 --> 00:39:34,600
Very good.



00:39:34,840 --> 00:39:36,680
Your provocation is working.



00:39:40,320 --> 00:39:41,600
Lu Ping, come here.



00:39:46,240 --> 00:39:47,040
What's the matter?



00:39:48,800 --> 00:39:50,360
For you to succeed,



00:39:51,320 --> 00:39:53,120
I have prepared specifically



00:39:53,400 --> 00:39:55,280
an affordable gift for you.



00:39:55,520 --> 00:39:56,640
You have a gift for me?



00:40:04,600 --> 00:40:05,400
Master.



00:40:06,000 --> 00:40:07,800
Use it when you pray
for our founding master.



00:40:08,080 --> 00:40:09,040
I don't need it.



00:40:10,760 --> 00:40:11,840
Since the day in the tower,



00:40:11,920 --> 00:40:13,240
I broke one of the chains.



00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:14,720
The usage of my soul power



00:40:14,800 --> 00:40:16,080
isn't limited
to burning one joss stick anymore.



00:40:16,680 --> 00:40:19,000
I think I can handle the convention.



00:40:21,920 --> 00:40:23,520
I already taught you



00:40:24,040 --> 00:40:25,520
most of the things I know.



00:40:25,800 --> 00:40:28,920
Only this Kaifeng City can teach you



00:40:29,000 --> 00:40:30,080
the remaining things.



00:40:32,120 --> 00:40:33,160
Do you guys smell it?



00:40:33,840 --> 00:40:34,920
The Shanhai Gang?



00:40:36,400 --> 00:40:37,320
Shanhai Gang again.



00:40:37,440 --> 00:40:38,240
Other than escaping,



00:40:38,320 --> 00:40:39,480
can you think of something else?



00:40:39,560 --> 00:40:40,360
It's congee.



00:40:40,520 --> 00:40:42,960
The most famous congee in Kaifeng City.



00:40:47,760 --> 00:40:48,600
Young Master.



00:40:48,720 --> 00:40:50,080
The Soul Combat Convention is near.



00:40:50,320 --> 00:40:52,760
Master reminded me to be wary
of your work-sleep balance.



00:40:53,040 --> 00:40:55,400
Where do you want to have your meal today?



00:40:56,440 --> 00:40:59,080
Not meeting Sangsang,
my heart is filled with sadness.



00:40:59,880 --> 00:41:01,560
Let's have something light.



00:41:05,040 --> 00:41:06,040
[Yuyangji Congee Store]



00:41:11,360 --> 00:41:12,880
Honorable guests of the Qin family,



00:41:13,240 --> 00:41:14,720
although our shop is small,



00:41:15,000 --> 00:41:15,960
this crab congee



00:41:16,200 --> 00:41:18,360
is the one and only in Kaifeng City.



00:41:18,720 --> 00:41:20,000
Please enjoy.



00:41:20,560 --> 00:41:22,680
River crab, Japonica rice, and parsley.



00:41:22,800 --> 00:41:23,600
Nothing more,



00:41:23,720 --> 00:41:24,600
nothing less.



00:41:25,240 --> 00:41:26,280
Martial arts practitioners



00:41:26,760 --> 00:41:28,560
shouldn't crave for good food.



00:41:29,120 --> 00:41:30,080
Xifan.



00:41:30,520 --> 00:41:32,560
Martial arts practitioners aren't monks.



00:41:33,080 --> 00:41:33,880
Here.



00:41:43,960 --> 00:41:44,920
Zhao Xifan.



00:41:45,320 --> 00:41:46,760
I'm cultivating soul of Pivot.



00:41:46,880 --> 00:41:47,760
Perception is my focus,



00:41:48,000 --> 00:41:48,880
so not only must I eat,



00:41:49,000 --> 00:41:50,080
I must eat good food.



00:41:50,640 --> 00:41:53,160
Nobody wants to live
an ascetic life like you.



00:41:58,960 --> 00:42:00,040
But it's odd.



00:42:00,480 --> 00:42:01,560
In this congee restaurant,



00:42:01,840 --> 00:42:03,680
why is there a woman who reeks of alcohol?



00:42:03,920 --> 00:42:05,480
It ruins the congee's delicate taste.



00:42:17,000 --> 00:42:18,360
What is that smell? It's so familiar.



00:42:18,680 --> 00:42:21,000
Sir, I want another bowl of congee.



00:42:22,880 --> 00:42:23,920
Excuse me.



00:42:24,040 --> 00:42:24,920
I'm coming.



00:42:29,080 --> 00:42:30,120
Do you have private seats?



00:42:31,040 --> 00:42:31,840
Sir.



00:42:32,440 --> 00:42:33,840
Our private seats are occupied.



00:42:34,120 --> 00:42:35,800
Do you mind sitting here?



00:42:36,560 --> 00:42:37,920
I just reached Kaifeng



00:42:38,040 --> 00:42:39,320
and I came to your restaurant.



00:42:39,680 --> 00:42:41,720
But you actually told me
that there's no private seat.



00:42:42,120 --> 00:42:43,760
Don't you feel bad for all my sweat



00:42:43,880 --> 00:42:45,320
and tears to come here?



00:42:46,040 --> 00:42:48,040
Enemies often cross each other's path,
don't you think so?



00:42:48,920 --> 00:42:49,800
Sir.



00:42:50,320 --> 00:42:51,640
Do you know who my father is?



00:42:52,000 --> 00:42:53,840
Have you heard of Chan State's Wei family?



00:42:54,200 --> 00:42:56,120
I'm the young master of the Wei family.



00:43:00,800 --> 00:43:01,840
This place reeks of alcohol.



00:43:02,080 --> 00:43:03,400
How could we eat?



00:43:04,240 --> 00:43:05,040
Sir,



00:43:05,280 --> 00:43:07,440
Kaifeng doesn't care about the Wei family.



00:43:07,840 --> 00:43:10,480
Not to mention, my private seats



00:43:10,880 --> 00:43:12,640
are occupied by honorable guests.



00:43:12,960 --> 00:43:13,760
Honorable guests?



00:43:18,320 --> 00:43:19,960
Are those the honorable guests
you mentioned?



00:43:20,600 --> 00:43:23,160
No matter what, I want the private seats.



00:43:24,200 --> 00:43:25,040
Wei Hu.



00:43:25,360 --> 00:43:26,760
Throw them out.



00:43:27,240 --> 00:43:28,880
Mr. Wei, Master instructed us



00:43:28,960 --> 00:43:31,200
that we must keep
a low profile in Kaifeng.



00:43:31,600 --> 00:43:33,000
If you won't, I'll do it myself.



00:43:38,000 --> 00:43:38,800
Sir.



00:43:38,880 --> 00:43:39,680
Move aside!



00:43:40,080 --> 00:43:41,360
Sir, don't smash anything. Sir!



00:43:41,440 --> 00:43:42,240
Go!



00:43:46,440 --> 00:43:48,120
Excuse me, this is your congee.

